Release x.y.z (YYYY-MM-DD)
==========================

Release 0.4.0 (2016-11-28)
==========================
2016-11-28 Bert van Hall <bert.vanhall@avionic-design.de>
  * SW-Version 0.4.0
  * usb_eeprom:
    - fix verification failures by adding small delays
    - switch to libusb-1.0 API
    - add function to detect EEPROMs on supported hubs

  * hub-ctrl:
    - split out and rework command line options
    - add device scanning mode
    - add version printing option
    - improve error messages
    - lots of smaller code improvements and cleanups

  * build:
    - fix missing header and linker flags
    - improve default silence
    - add and distribute udev rule

  * tests:
    - use mockup to cover libusb-1.0 dependency
    - add tests for usb_eeprom_write()
    - add tests for usb_eeprom_support()
    - add auto mode for BlueTooth test script

Release 0.2.0 (2016-11-08)
==========================

2016-11-08 Meike Vocke <meike.vocke@avionic-design.de>
  * SW-Version 0.2.0
  * Initial Release of the hub-ctrl software
